---
---

<section class="services rx">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="services-header">
      <span class="svc-eyebrow">How We Work</span>
      <h2 class="svc-title">Six Core Capabilities</h2>
      <p class="svc-sub">We help law firms fix the broken chain from lead to retained client.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <a href="/services/data-analysis-for-law-firms" class="service-card rxl d1">
        <div class="svc-num">01</div>
        <h3>Data Analysis</h3>
        <p>Build unified dashboards showing cost per retained client across all channels. Stop optimizing for vanity metrics.</p>
        <div class="svc-arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/agency-management-for-law-firms" class="service-card rxl d2">
        <div class="svc-num">02</div>
        <h3>Agency Management</h3>
        <p>Audit vendors, align them on unified KPIs, and make them accountable for retained client outcomes.</p>
        <div class="svc-arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/intake-process-optimization" class="service-card rxr d1">
        <div class="svc-num">03</div>
        <h3>Intake Optimization</h3>
        <p>Fix the 53% lead leak between inquiry and consultation. Redesign workflows, implement technology, train your team.</p>
        <div class="svc-arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/strategic-marketing-for-law-firms" class="service-card rxr d2">
        <div class="svc-num">04</div>
        <h3>Strategic Marketing</h3>
        <p>Replace reactive vendor pitches with a 12-month playbook tied to retained client growth targets.</p>
        <div class="svc-arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/always-publishing-always-ranking/" class="service-card featured rxl d3">
        <span class="svc-badge">NEW</span>
        <div class="svc-num">05</div>
        <h3>Always Publishing. Always Ranking.</h3>
        <p>Automated content engine for law firms. Daily blog posts, daily social distribution, clean technical SEO — without your team touching it.</p>
        <div class="svc-arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/services" class="service-card rxr d3">
        <div class="svc-num">06</div>
        <h3>Consulting</h3>
        <p>Expert guidance on marketing strategy, vendor selection, budget allocation, and growth planning for your firm.</p>
        <div class="svc-arrow">→</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .services-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .svc-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .svc-title {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 56px);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .svc-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--sub);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .service-card {
    position: relative;
    padding: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FAFAF5 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.15);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .service-card.featured {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFFBF0 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
    border-color: rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.45);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1);
  }

  .service-card.featured:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 56px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.22);
  }

  .svc-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 18px;
    right: 18px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 4px 9px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .svc-num {
    font-family: var(--bar);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 64px;
    color: rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.15);
    line-height: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--sub);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .svc-arrow {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 800;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover .svc-arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
